      "value": "<h3 id=\"TreasureAOVs-AOVsandLPEs\">AOVs and LPEs</h3><p>LPEs in this project are an import from a previous project (Rivendell fan art), and the beauty of Katana is that you can use nodes, or even a whole template between projects, and also between version of the software (for instance, the LPEs group were ported from Katana v3.5 and this project was done using Katana v6.0 and also tried the same Katana script with v6.5).</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"scene_nodeGraph_v01.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391684/scene_nodeGraph_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590721189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=486\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391684/scene_nodeGraph_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590721189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"894\" data-width=\"1396\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657424548\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"scene_nodeGraph_v01.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391684\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"16a7d806-6d83-4a0e-a75e-70e77e3db5f3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391684/scene_nodeGraph_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590721189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1396&amp;height=894 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391684/scene_nodeGraph_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590721189&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=486 1x\"></sp